Contemporary management of metastatic bone disease: tips and tools of the trade 
for general practitioners.

Quinn RH(1), Randall RL, Benevenia J, Berven SH, Raskin KA.

Author information:
(1)Professor and Chair, Department of Orthopaedic Surgery, University of Texas 
Health Science Center, San Antonio, Texas.

Metastatic bone disease has a significant effect on a patient's mortality and 
